    <rigor-reason>Tags include `bff-api` + `ai` + `playbook-engine`; modifies `PlaybookExecutionEngine.cs` + `NodeType` enum (load-bearing AI orchestration); backward-compat invariant; FULL per task-execute Step 0.5.</rigor-reason>
